  +-- phantom-frontmatter-ghost-wstunnel.service
  +-- phantom-frontmatter-ghost-egress.service

  SQLite schema:
    Single database file: data/frontmatter.db. One table per
    module. Every table has the same shape:

        CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS <module> (
            key   TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
            value TEXT NOT NULL
        );

  Tables after setup init:

    setup
      backend_ip            "203.0.113.10"
      backend_port          "51820"
      tls_cert_path         "/opt/phantom-frontmatter/secrets/tls_cert"
      tls_key_path          "/opt/phantom-frontmatter/secrets/tls_key"
      wstunnel_binary_path  "/opt/phantom-frontmatter/bin/wstunnel"
      wstunnel_version      "10.5.2"
      socat_binary_path     "/usr/bin/socat"
      initialized_at        "2026-01-01T00:00:00+00:00"

    ghost
      wstunnel_listen_port  "443"
      wstunnel_secret       "<43-char URL-safe random>"
      loopback_port         "51820"


Backend requirements:

  The backend UDP endpoint requires no changes. A reachable
  UDP port is sufficient; frontmatter sends datagrams from
  front's own outbound socket.


